---
title: Black Bean and Charred Bell Pepper Quesadillas with Caramelized Onion
description: I don’t know about you, but we find it impossible to resist gooey, melted mozzarella - especially when it comes inside crisp flour tortillas with refried beans and bright red peppers. A light side salad is the perfect counterpart to these satisfying veggie quesadillas.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/black-bean-quesadillas-99a95db3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/black-bean-and-charred-bell-pepp-97683dba.pdf
